PN,41601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778839648
OL,3,CMan killed student with 21cm knife
OL,4,Cafter saying 'I'm a bad man', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA first-year university student was
OL,8,Fstabbed to death by a man who is shown
OL,9,Fon phone footage saying "I'm a bad
OL,10,Fman" before the fatal incident, a
OL,11,Fcourt has heard.
OL,13,FVickrum Digwa is on trial at
OL,14,FSouthampton Crown Court charged with
OL,15,Fthe murder of Henry Nowak, 18, from
OL,16,FChafford Hundred, Essex, in Belmont
OL,17,FRoad, Southampton, on December 3 2025.
OL,26,@qD@YOUrD@DO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
