OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778839648
OL,3,CMan killed student with 21cm knife
OL,4,Cafter saying 'I'm a bad man', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe 23-year-old is also charged with
OL,8,Fcarrying a knife in public and his
OL,9,Fmother, Kiran Kaur, 53, is accused of
OL,10,Fassisting an offender by removing a
OL,11,Fweapon from the murder scene.
OL,13,FNicholas Lobbenberg KC, prosecuting,
OL,14,Ftold the jury the accountancy and
OL,15,Ffinance student was sending Snapchat
OL,16,Fvideos to friends as he was walking
OL,17,Fhome from a night out with his
OL,18,Ffootball team when the fatal incident
OL,19,Fhappened.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778839648
OL,3,CMan killed student with 21cm knife
OL,4,Cafter saying 'I'm a bad man', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe said Mr Nowak had drunk less than
OL,8,Fthe drink-drive limit during the
OL,9,Fevening.
OL,11,F"His phone captures the moment he met
OL,12,FVickrum Digwa," Mr Lobbenberg said.
OL,13,F"Vickrum Digwa was carrying an
OL,14,Fextremely large knife in a sheath
OL,15,Fopenly displayed over his clothing.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@OO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778839648
OL,3,CMan killed student with 21cm knife
OL,4,Cafter saying 'I'm a bad man', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"At half-past midnight that night,
OL,8,FHenry was dead, he had been fatally
OL,9,Fstabbed by Vickrum Digwa using that
OL,10,Fknife, the knife that Vickrum Digwa
OL,11,Fhas chosen to carry out on to the
OL,12,Fstreet.
OL,14,F"The killing wasn't seen by anyone
OL,15,Fother than Henry and Vickrum Digwa,
OL,16,Fthe neighbours heard the aftermath as
OL,17,FHenry complained that he had been
OL,18,Fstabbed and that he was dying,
OL,19,Ftragically Henry was right on both
OL,20,Fcounts.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778839648
OL,3,CMan killed student with 21cm knife
OL,4,Cafter saying 'I'm a bad man', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"After he had been stabbed, Henry
OL,8,Fclimbed on to a bin and over a fence
OL,9,Fto try and escape but he had already
OL,10,Fbeen fatally wounded and there was a
OL,11,Fblood trail on the street which
OL,12,Fdemonstrates that he must have been
OL,13,Fstabbed before he climbed on to the
OL,14,Fbin and over the fence.
OL,16,F"Vickrum Digwa chose to aggressively
OL,17,Fpursue him."
OL,19,FThe prosecutor said a video of the
OL,20,Fincident was found on Mr Nowak's phone
OL,21,Fwhich was discovered in Digwa's pocket.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778839648
OL,3,CMan killed student with 21cm knife
OL,4,Cafter saying 'I'm a bad man', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FIn the video, played to the jury, Mr
OL,8,FNowak can be heard saying "Hello car"
OL,9,Fand singing to himself before yawning,
OL,10,Fwith the footage then cutting to show
OL,11,FDigwa walking away from him.
OL,13,FMr Nowak is then heard saying: "Innit
OL,14,Fbad man, what bad man. You're a bad
OL,15,Fman, say you're a bad man, go on."
OL,17,FDigwa replied: "I am a bad man" with
OL,18,FMr Nowak then saying "Are you a b...",
OL,19,Fbefore the footage cuts off.
OL,26,@pD@[OUpD@eO]uD@`OUwD@bO]yD@POUyD@_O]zD@
OL,26,AVOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
