FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778839648
OL,3,CMan killed student with 21cm knife
OL,4,Cafter saying 'I'm a bad man', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Lobbenberg said the defendant's
OL,8,Ffather and brother were at the scene
OL,9,Fshortly afterwards along with his
OL,10,Fmother, who was captured on video
OL,11,Ffootage taking the knife back to their
OL,12,Ffamily home in nearby St Denys Road
OL,13,Fwhere it was later found by police.
OL,15,FThe prosecutor said Digwa denied at
OL,16,Fthe scene stabbing Mr Nowak and added:
OL,17,F"Vickrum Digwa said he had been
OL,18,Fracially abused and attacked by a
OL,19,Fdrunken man. Henry protested he hadn't
OL,20,Fattacked Vickrum Digwa and he had been
OL,21,Fstabbed."
OL,26,@yD@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778839648
OL,3,CMan killed student with 21cm knife
OL,4,Cafter saying 'I'm a bad man', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Lobbenberg said: "He didn't seek
OL,8,Fhelp for the man he had injured with
OL,9,Fhis sizeable knife, instead he accused
OL,10,Fhim of being a racist and being drunk."
OL,12,FHe added that police initially
OL,13,Fhandcuffed Mr Nowak and started giving
OL,14,Fhim first aid when he then collapsed.
OL,26,@oD@UOUrD@gO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778839648
OL,3,CMan killed student with 21cm knife
OL,4,Cafter saying 'I'm a bad man', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe said: "Shortly afterwards Henry
OL,8,Fbecame unconscious, then police began
OL,9,Fto set to work to give him first aid
OL,10,Fand summon an ambulance, a doctor flew
OL,11,Fin by helicopter but there was nothing
OL,12,Fthat could be done to save Henry and
OL,13,Fhe was declared dead."
OL,15,FMr Lobbenberg said a post-mortem
OL,16,Fexamination found Mr Nowak suffered
OL,17,Ffour stab wounds and a cut to his jaw,
OL,18,Fwith two of the wounds to the back of
OL,19,Fhis legs.
OL,26,@oD@JOUuD@VO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778839648
OL,3,CMan killed student with 21cm knife
OL,4,Cafter saying 'I'm a bad man', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Lobbenberg added that analysis of
OL,8,Fthe knife found blood and fatty tissue
OL,9,Fmatched to Mr Nowak and hairs from
OL,10,FDigwa as well as DNA from Kaur on the
OL,11,Fsheath.
OL,13,FThe prosecutor said as well as the
OL,14,Fshastar ` the Punjabi word for weapon
OL,15,For knife ` which had a 21cm blade,
OL,16,FDigwa had a kirpan knife around his
OL,17,Fneck and under his clothing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778839648
OL,3,CMan killed student with 21cm knife
OL,4,Cafter saying 'I'm a bad man', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe said: "Sikhism obliges male
OL,8,Ffollowers of the faith to carry and
OL,9,Fwear certain items, these include a
OL,10,Fwooden comb, a metal bangle and what
OL,11,Fis called a kirpan, a ceremonial knife.
OL,13,F"That small kirpan satisfies any
OL,14,Freligious obligation a Sikh may have
OL,15,Fto carry a blade and Mr Vickrum Digwa
OL,16,Fwas carrying that under his clothing
OL,17,Fand around his neck."
OL,19,FHe added: "Mr Digwa was choosing to
OL,20,Fcarry on the streets of Southampton a
OL,21,Fvery large 21cm bladed knife."
OL,26,@oD@JOUuD@AOUyD@UO]{D@KOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778839648
OL,3,CMan killed student with 21cm knife
OL,4,Cafter saying 'I'm a bad man', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Lobbenberg said that Digwa answered
OL,8,Fno comment in police interview but
OL,9,Fgave a prepared statement saying that
OL,10,F"Henry Nowak had subjected him to a
OL,11,Fdrunken, racist attack" and accused
OL,12,Fhim of knocking his turban off and
OL,13,Fgrabbing his hair.
OL,15,FHe also stated that it was with his
OL,16,Fhair in front of his eyes that he
OL,17,F"stabbed out twice with his kirpan"
OL,18,Fand acted in self-defence.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@WO]yD@AOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778839648
OL,3,CMan killed student with 21cm knife
OL,4,Cafter saying 'I'm a bad man', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe prosecutor said that video footage
OL,8,Fof Mr Nowak climbing over a fence
OL,9,Fshowed Digwa with hair in a tight bun
OL,10,Fbut then when police had arrived, his
OL,11,Fhair was down.
OL,13,FMr Lobbenberg said: "Why has he put
OL,14,Fhis hair down for the arrival of the
OL,15,Fpolice, what does that tell you about
OL,16,Fwhat he is telling them?"
OL,26,@uD@UOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778839648
OL,3,CMan killed student with 21cm knife
OL,4,Cafter saying 'I'm a bad man', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FJeremy Wainwright KC, representing
OL,8,FDigwa, told the jury the larger of the
OL,9,Fknives carried by the defendant was
OL,10,Fless than 9in long, which was within
OL,11,Fthe permitted length of kirpan that a
OL,12,FSikh is allowed to carry for religious
OL,13,Freasons.
OL,15,FHe also asked the jurors to think
OL,16,Fabout who started the incident between
OL,17,Fthe two men, and said they would need
OL,18,Fto consider whether the prosecution
OL,19,Fcan prove the defendant was not the
OL,20,Fvictim of a racist attack from Mr
OL,21,FNowak.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778839648
OL,3,CMan killed student with 21cm knife
OL,4,Cafter saying 'I'm a bad man', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Wainwright added: "Was there a
OL,8,Fdeliberate intention by Vickrum Digwa
OL,9,Fto inflict really serious harm or kill
OL,10,FHenry Nowak when he used his kirpan,
OL,11,For was he acting in the heat of the
OL,12,Fmoment in self-defence?"
OL,14,FDigwa and Kaur deny the charges and
OL,15,Fthe trial continues.
OL,26,@oD@VOUtD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/16
